  • Classes in org.miloss.fgsms.plugins.sla used by org.miloss.fgsms.common 
    Class and Description
    AlertContainer
    A simple structure to make the processing of alerting easier fgsms processes alerts asynchronously either via a Singleton message processor that runs in a separate thread or via Jboss's Work Manager, depending on what's available.
